{"tid":1637514,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"而根據opta統計，蘇斯克查轉正以來僅取得17個聯賽積分，在同期的英超僅排倒數第4。","createTime":"2019-10-08T04:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T05:28:44.000Z","uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0e180a055b6a253e3ed8316254319f12d9c5458c","tid":1637514,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:11:22.000Z","msg":"香港時間10月6日，英超第8輪，曼聯作客0-1不敵紐卡素聯，開季8輪僅取得9分。<br />\n<br />\n  據統計，自從蘇斯克查轉正以來，曼聯在英超聯賽中僅僅拿到了17個聯賽積分，同期他們的死敵利物浦則取得了17場勝利，曼聯在聯賽中取得的分數和利物浦的勝場一樣多。<br />\n<br />\n  而根據opta統計，蘇斯克查轉正以來僅取得17個聯賽積分，在同期的英超僅排倒數第4。<br />\n<br />\n  下一輪聯賽，曼聯與利物浦將迎來直接對話。<br />\n<br />\n降班不是夢"},{"pid":"d17b1d6224f2fb1ceaedbccd7e3d88ea0d939bcf","tid":1637514,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:20:51.000Z","msg":"同球員時代一樣都係後備勁過正選<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6499f75cca6751ff85bcc1daa2d19262fa9517","tid":1637514,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d17b1d6224f2fb1ceaedbccd7e3d88ea0d939bcf","tid":1637514,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:20:51.000Z","msg":"同球員時代一樣都係後備勁過正選<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:07:48.000Z","msg":"後備殺手，10分鐘入4球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n99歐聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d75f7486c679fd173333cc7dd4d2118f6119b99","tid":1637514,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:28:44.000Z","msg":"原來都有第四名"}]}